 B，仲有個 C 起梗<br />\n<br />\n遲下應該成個 D 嘅國內線扔晒過去 B 同 C<br />\n<br />\nD, E, F 全部做晒國際線，到時應該仲多甩漏。<br />\n<br />\n佢自己唔保障自己啫，啲轉機時間唔夠兩個鐘都照俾你一張機票買，去程一 Delay 就仆街。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:50:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.aeroflot.ru/ru-en/information/airport/transit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aeroflot.ru%2Fru-en%2Finformation%2Fairport%2Ftransit&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=aef81838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aeroflot.ru/ru-en/information/airport/transit</a><br />\n佢個minimum connection time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"試過我買國內線要轉機<br />\n<br />\n佢朝早班機取消改咗晏啲飛，結果第二班機同第一班機相隔時間係半個鐘，但都無通知我要改第二班機時間。<br />\n<br />\n30分鐘點轉機呀？<br />\n<br />\n結果我要自己打電話上去改。"},{"pid":"8b404dede2a7131dd978a56ac474a21302451679","tid":1001152,"uid":38305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"airport tax 200 usd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc9438a759065014e8cdcd3aab7e6479a071e3e","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b404dede2a7131dd978a56ac474a21302451679","tid":1001152,"uid":38305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"airport tax 200 usd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"Fuel surcharge per flight segment 嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1jaw2ZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jaw2ZD.jpg&h=15889f8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98c81ee63e732ac6ef6b8dbb386451628e302196","tid":1001152,"uid":38305,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzKNBmz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzKNBmz.png&h=f43a962f&s={SIZE}\" />搵過幾個都無貴到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4cdfabb92d876e3099ef66270e6ac8cdf630e1","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"98c81ee63e732ac6ef6b8dbb386451628e302196","tid":1001152,"uid":38305,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzKNBmz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzKNBmz.png&h=f43a962f&s={SIZE}\" />搵過幾個都無貴到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"因為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2864ac7cb6e42fd043644ef18165a07dcc4affda","tid":1001152,"uid":81264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"近年搭佢去歐洲貪佢平同快<br />\n早幾年如果轉機時間趕<br />\n你要自己打尖同counter d人講<br />\n近年會有職員係排隊位叫啲趕飛機既插隊<br />\n唔知係咪世界盃關係<br />\n機場好似仲擴建近<br />\n上年要搭成廿十分鐘車去個爛地上機<br />\n不過駁歐洲機有啲係舊式細機<br />\n又搖又chock<br />\n以前後生就話頂得住<br />\n以家心血少啲都唔掂<br />\n如果加價就要諗過啦"},{"pid":"9a4de6cba92279efda183d575e7c979bd5a644e5","tid":1001152,"uid":59041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:25:09.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得唔安全，平時見到平都唔敢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd63d803ecd5c6e93b7ab6ee040eecd771157ecc","tid":1001152,"uid":67432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"行李真係個個都屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df0b1abeba180e49e010e9e15c582b0e2aaeb3e","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd63d803ecd5c6e93b7ab6ee040eecd771157ecc","tid":1001152,"uid":67432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"行李真係個個都屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"太短時間轉機，有機會跟唔切轉<br />\n<br />\n太多時間轉機，有機會老鼠爆喼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ccfca57c6247bc327c111d42edd23e57845680","tid":1001152,"uid":35365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"上次世盃中撚晒大伏<br />\n香港經SVO轉機去LED但係得個半鐘轉機時間<br />\n過入境關口撞正前面有架支那機早一步到排到嘔<br />\n班俄佬唔到最尾一分鐘都唔肯畀你班趕轉機既排另一條隊check咗先<br />\n仲要行勁遠去另一個terminal<br />\n結果趕唔到connection flight<br />\n要即場買過張下幾班既機票成8000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd2ff86c940725d400b5b0dc1a8056d0d124adc","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79ccfca57c6247bc327c111d42edd23e57845680","tid":1001152,"uid":35365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"上次世盃中撚晒大伏<br />\n香港經SVO轉機去LED但係得個半鐘轉機時間<br />\n過入境關口撞正前面有架支那機早一步到排到嘔<br />\n班俄佬唔到最尾一分鐘都唔肯畀你班趕轉機既排另一條隊check咗先<br />\n仲要行勁遠去另一個terminal<br />\n結果趕唔到connection flight<br />\n要即場買過張下幾班既機票成8000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"你唔係同一個 PNR 買？<br />\n<br />\n無得免費出過張俾你？<br />\n<br />\n排隊真係要靠自己，無得靠啲仆街職員，點鳩你打尖，但佢自己又唔肯去帶你去，咁我不如直接去到最前叫人讓我先啦。"},{"pid":"1629a57057eb00ed7da235c072262aaea9f314be","tid":1001152,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd2ff86c940725d400b5b0dc1a8056d0d124adc","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79ccfca57c6247bc327c111d42edd23e57845680","tid":1001152,"uid":35365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"上次世盃中撚晒大伏<br />\n香港經SVO轉機去LED但係得個半鐘轉機時間<br />\n過入境關口撞正前面有架支那機早一步到排到嘔<br />\n班俄佬唔到最尾一分鐘都唔肯畀你班趕轉機既排另一條隊check咗先<br />\n仲要行勁遠去另一個terminal<br />\n結果趕唔到connection flight<br />\n要即場買過張下幾班既機票成8000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-