/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"無晒假<br />\n<br />\n今年去4個長 trip，應該都無晒假。<br />\n<br />\n聖誕都應該唔夠假去，買咗先算。<br />\n<br />\n玩快閃。"},{"pid":"e88be1a0a83b235054d0d94ae630b4b9f13afbfb","tid":1001152,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb2c15ec1bf11ac7ef864503ed9ca41139b63397","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f931cf1c9e40849aa0cd688c1eeff8583f4aa8de","tid":1001152,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5320006131f789342f671765e2fe549066b51d5d","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"你唔好迫我啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"無晒假<br />\n<br />\n今年去4個長 trip，應該都無晒假。<br />\n<br />\n聖誕都應該唔夠假去，買咗先算。<br />\n<br />\n玩快閃。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:16:51.000Z","msg":"俄佬有咩玩？<br />\n7月諗9日St Petersburg + Moscow <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本諗會唔會去埋Konigsburg 或者 海參崴<br />\n但太貴 算數"},{"pid":"b42b4bac5c9b0d4d2fb157a1b0ef0925bcd0a657","tid":1001152,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:17:43.000Z","msg":"Konigsberg / Kaliningrad"},{"pid":"8c161275c2cb477e0393e276738c59362bb02830","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b42b4bac5c9b0d4d2fb157a1b0ef0925bcd0a657","tid":1001152,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:17:43.000Z","msg":"Konigsberg / Kaliningrad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯好多城市都去過，呢次未 plan 嘅，睇到時有咩內陸機平機票就諗去邊。<br />\n<br />\n又或者同莫斯科唔太遠嘅地方，莫斯科好多冷門嘢都未去。<br />\n<br />\n我自己就鍾意去啲軍事或舊蘇聯嘅博物館，太耐歷史嗰啲又唔算好大興趣。<br />\n<br />\n你唔打俄名我都知你講加里寧格勒<br />\n<br />\n內陸機唔算好貴咋喎，飛落去。<br />\n<br />\n你第一次去就去啲大路嘢先啦。"},{"pid":"ce22ae27cf6a6dfed2dcbb2e1cd59b2485ea5006","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae41f11ccc01ea0909897db1dce22b7bca6060d4","tid":1001152,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa50cced94bca8e50374de48e6d8b59c011d0437","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe2566219d38c4fc7b42f1adade9e17f0960b9a4","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"聖誕機票開始賣啦，暫時可以買到28號回程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:20:03.000Z","msg":"連登力量<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"出發日期唔同喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:47:45.000Z","msg":"呢個同日期來回。<br />\n<br />\n最 Update 價錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hi7LFb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHi7LFb9.jpg&h=69684f99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1da7a1141cfd687734bc2f2b58bc812ab271341","tid":1001152,"uid":57582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"可以坐俄航去MSQ㗎？<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯去白俄唔係當內陸線,<br />\n過唔到白俄移民局，<br />\n去到MSQ會當非法入境？"},{"pid":"89115c2ca0c442a608110007407000ba848ef35f","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1da7a1141cfd687734bc2f2b58bc812ab271341","tid":1001152,"uid":57582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"可以坐俄航去MSQ㗎？<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯去白俄唔係當內陸線,<br />\n過唔到白俄移民局，<br />\n去到MSQ會當非法入境？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯入境轉機，再出境嗰陣，你要 keep 番張出入境卡。<br />\n<br />\n佢正常會睇你登機證，見你去明思克，唔會收你張過出入境卡。<br />\n<br />\n你去到白羅斯就要靠佢嚟出境。<br />\n<br />\n不過，政策有無再改，唔知。<br />\n<br />\n聖誕節嗰陣，問過香港地勤都話仲要入境俄羅斯先可以轉機去白羅斯。"},{"pid":"007d1f672db28e90eb2e307d3df68ccf8db7d0d7","tid":1001152,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"去歐洲要平都唔洗選俄航啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家最平緊係坐酷航 窮撚首選"},{"pid":"f23eba74b0b3c8a37742036b0b764e6f81613140","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"007d1f672db28e90eb2e307d3df68ccf8db7d0d7","tid":1001152,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"去歐洲要平都唔洗選俄航啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家最平緊係坐酷航 窮撚首選"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"你又搵啲大時大節出嚟，睇下有幾平囉。<br />\n<br />\n要日日有機喎。"},{"pid":"52f68624535fb001c9555c708365890f954456bd","tid":1001152,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T17:02:37.000Z","msg":"今日班機好撚正。<br />\n<br />\ndelay 唔算好多，香港遲九個字飛，去到莫斯科降落都叫準時。<br />\n<br />\n但冇橋泊，等落機上巴士，上到巴士仲要喺跑道穿插慢行、由降落去到 Terminal 要九個字。<br />\n<br />\n去到 Terminal，原來送咗去 Terminal D，我都係第一次香港飛要去呢個 Terminal 。<br />\n<br />\n轉國際線人多到癲，入境就唔算多人，每條隊頂多六，七個人。<br />\n<br />\n國際轉機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkDOOoK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkDOOoK.jpg&h=6f15ae4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見有臺灣人過俄羅斯人護照通道又過得，我就跟埋過，好快就入咗境。<br />\n<br />\n去到行李帶，以降落計一個鐘，行李已經出咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRVEU3C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRVEU3C.jpg&h=2eff3c6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"260ddec6158b3197a906dcf8d35f4cd0eb098374","tid":1001152,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T20:21:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"676979033b249bc0ec1199956971dad513587782","tid":1001152,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df0b1abeba180e49e010e9e15c582b0e2aaeb3e","t